title: S12 Ep142: MonsterTalk
itunes:title: MonsterTalk
description:
Blake Smith is the host of a Science based podcast that investigates claims of Monsters and the unusual. We look at some of the truths and beliefs surrounding some of the most famous creatures reported around the world.
